{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399100/extras/objective.png?t=1737199022\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your job is to engineer and test weapons in our weapon simulation program. To ensure you have your engineering priorities right, damage requirements ramp up fast. Try not to kill yourself while engineering for maximal destruction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399100/extras/simulation.png?t=1737199022\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A top-down environment to test the effectiveness of your creations. Butter-smooth, fast-paced movement on violent synth beats allow you to dance around enemies, stabbing, smashing, and shooting them to bits. Aggression will be rewarded accordingly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399100/extras/Flashes_of_Chaos_explosive_SMG.gif?t=1737199022\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399100/extras/shop.png?t=1737199022\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A place to normalize your heartbeat and spend your hard-earned cash on essential engineering tools. Buy:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New cards to transform how your weapons work.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tools to merge, modify, and upgrade cards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Perks to maximize synergies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399100/extras/Flashes_of_Chaos_shop_loop.gif?t=1737199022\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399100/extras/inventory.png?t=1737199022\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The place where you engineer your weapons of choice. Place your collected and modified cards in weapon slots to customize their behavior. Use modifiers with triggers to chain cards together into massive combos or elegantly mix cards to unlock game-changing synergies. Do everything necessary to create total devastation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399100/extras/Flashes_of_chaos_inventory.gif?t=1737199022\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399100/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737199022","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399100/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737199022","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399100/d83530c7b018a529ce0d50febd5b1222c5ed9daa/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737199022","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399100/d83530c7b018a529ce0d50febd5b1222c5ed9daa/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737199022","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Violence, Blood, Dead Bodies"},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399100/extras/objective.png?t=1737199022\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your job is to engineer and test weapons in our weapon simulation program. To ensure you have your engineer